WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([s].[WorkshopId] = @__WorkshopId_0)
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]"

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]
    FROM [Content] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[SectionId] = @__SectionId_0)
    ORDER BY [c].[OrderNo]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[ContentId], [r].[CreaDate], [r].[CreaUser], [r].[IsActive], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[IsState], [r].[IsStatus], [r].[ModDate], [r].[ModUser], [r].[OrderNo], [r].[ReponseContent]

ORDER BY [t].[OrderNo], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]"

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]

    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[SectionId] = @__SectionId_0)
    ORDER BY [c].[OrderNo]
) AS [t]

    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryType], [w].[CreaDate], [w].[CreaUser], [w].[Definition], [w].[IsActive], [w].[IsDeleted], [w].[IsState], [w].[IsStatus], [w].[ModDate], [w].[ModUser], [w].[Name], [w].[OrderNo], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[PublishDuration]

    WHERE [w].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[WorkshopId] = [t].[Id]

ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]"

(DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[Definition], [s].[IsActive], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsState], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[WorkshopId], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryType], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[Definition], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[PublishDate], [t].[PublishDuration], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ContentData], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[DocVideoDesc], [t0].[DocumentType], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[ResponseType], [t0].[SectionId], [t0].[VideoLink]
FROM [Section] AS [s]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryType], [w].[CreaDate], [w].[CreaUser], [w].[Definition], [w].[IsActive], [w].[IsDeleted], [w].[IsState], [w].[IsStatus], [w].[ModDate], [w].[ModUser], [w].[Name], [w].[OrderNo], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[PublishDuration]
    FROM [Workshop] AS [w]
    WHERE [w].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[WorkshopId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]

    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ContentData], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[DocVideoDesc], [t].[DocumentType], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[ResponseType], [t].[SectionId], [t].[VideoLink], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ContentId], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[ReponseContent]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]
    FROM [Content] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[SectionId] = @__SectionId_0)
    ORDER BY [c].[OrderNo]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[ContentId], [r].[CreaDate], [r].[CreaUser], [r].[IsActive], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[IsState], [r].[IsStatus], [r].[ModDate], [r].[ModUser], [r].[OrderNo], [r].[ReponseContent]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]

    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[ContentId], [r].[CreaDate], [r].[CreaUser], [r].[IsActive], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[IsState], [r].[IsStatus], [r].[ModDate], [r].[ModUser], [r].[OrderNo], [r].[ReponseContent]
